docs {
  Aggregate business (tenant) counts for the SiteAdmin dashboard. Requires
  `business:read`. All counts exclude soft-deleted tenants.

  Returns in `data`:
  - `total` — all non-deleted tenants.
  - `active` — `subscriptionStatus = ACTIVE`.
  - `trial` — `subscriptionStatus = TRIALING`.
  - `suspended` — `subscriptionStatus = SUSPENDED`.

  `GRACE_PERIOD` / `CANCELLED` tenants count toward `total` only.
}
